description: All DB reads go through app/data/; use requireSession/requirePermission; prisma from @/lib/prisma
globs: "app/data/**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Data Layer

- **Location**: All DB reads go in `app/data/` (e.g. `data/admin/get-users.ts`, `data/hod/get-leave-requests.ts`).
- **Prisma**: `import prisma from "@/lib/prisma"`. Schema: `prisma/schema.prisma`.
- **Auth**: Use `requireSession()` from `app/data/session/require-session.ts`. Use `requirePermission()` from `app/data/permission/require-permission.ts` where needed.
- **Exports**: Export inferred row/entity types from data functions for use in table components (e.g. `GetLeaveRequestsType`).
